aaba9361986b8a798d8797b000b4175c46dbd5348f4df8f9deaa07af911482c89374db44683eb78571f649c34e19f80864a3c313c7ec6ff02cc4317db11c8517  config-postmarketos-stericsson.armv7
2bd8485ed91b552e802d80fd7c2e63ffc249530cc30e5c0be41fb0f64d20220bd0997514882ab59e8c7d9e5dd816c34d89363e18d0a78bd6c6692339010e2e74  v2_20251026_linus_walleij_drm_panel_fix_atomic_helper_induced_regressions.patch
"
